name: RED MASK T-shirt
description:
Jonny Wolf brings you another great graphic t-shirt Red MASK. All Awake and Dressed t-shirt's are photographic prints onto a top quality fashion fit white t-shirt. The t-shirt is 100% cotton with a fashionable dart neckline and an extremely soft touch and feel. As well as an out of seam detailing on the side of the t-shirt. We use Direct to Garment Printing to ensure no cracking or fading. All our T-shirts are printed to a high standard. each t-shirt comes with a Jonny Wolf exclusive signature on the front corner of the t-shirt. 


We also offer Free UK delivery on every item. We ship World wide as well, see details below for prices.  

Washing instructions

• Do not bleach
• Do not iron on the print
• Wash inside out
• Do not dry clean
• Machine wash at 30 degrees 

We appreciate your support and your helping a independent brand grow.

Any questions drop us a mail at info@awakeanddressed.com and we'll be happy to answer them.
